item.title: EP 139 - Are Grey Aliens Evolved From Dolphins?
item.itunes:title: Are Grey Aliens Evolved From Dolphins?
item.description:
Today we take a leap of faith as we meet 5 people who survived plane crashes without a parachute, and then we examine the so-crazy-it-might-be-true conspiracy that Grey Aliens are actually evolved dolphins.

Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

Help Promote Dead Rabbit!

Dual Flyer
https://i.imgur.com/OhuoI2v.jpg

"As Above" Flyer 
https://i.imgur.com/yobMtUp.jpg

 

Plane crashes are a horrifying experience. I would assume, I’ve never been in one. But these five people have and they all survived without a parachute!

And then we take look at the idea that aliens are not from out of the world but from under our seas. Are the Grey Aliens we see in popular culture really just a genetic offshoot from dolphins?
